texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: If you receive the following error, your PIX does not have a key set up for use with SSH:
texts.text: If you receive the following error, your PIX does not have a key set up for use with SSH:

texts.label: code
texts.orig:
Type help or '?' for a list of available commands.
pix>
Cannot select private key
texts.text:
Type help or '?' for a list of available commands.
pix>
Cannot select private key

texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: Regenerating the key can be done by executing the following:
texts.text: Regenerating the key can be done by executing the following:

texts.label: code
texts.orig:
conf t
ca zeroize rsa
ca generate rsa key 1024
ca save all
write mem
reload
texts.text:
conf t
ca zeroize rsa
ca generate rsa key 1024
ca save all
write mem
reload
